      "content": "i feel like i've been walking for so long and the trail just... it doesn't go anywhere anymore. it's like i've reached the edge of the world and there's nothing left but this heavy, grey fog and a cliff that just drops into nothingness. the path is gone. there's nowhere left to step.",
